Vi Cheat Sheet

:w 	Save
:x 	Save & Exit
:q 	Exit if no changes made
:q! 	Exit & discard any changes

Shift zz = :wq

/search	find the word you write after /



G 	End of file
gg	Start of document
dd 	Delete current line
D 	Delete the rest of line

U 	Undo all changes to line





:set nu 	   order with numbers does not save numbers tepe


*****

# cat -n 10 filename 	take you line 10
